.TP
.B \-U
Unsafe mode.
.
This will enable tha followin requests:
.BR open ,
.BR opena ,
.BR pso ,
.BR sy ,
and
.BR pi .
For securitizzle reasons, these potentially fucked up requests is disabled
otherwise.
