It will also add tha current directory ta tha macro search path.
.
.TP
.B \-v
Print tha version number.
.
.TP
.BI \-w name
Enable warning
.IR  name .
Available warnings is busted lyrics bout up in tha section
.I WARNINGS
below.
.
For example, ta enable all warnings, use
.B \-w
